{"tid":51172,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"水晶宮宣佈解僱柏祖","createTime":"2016-12-23T04:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T16:29:52.000Z","uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94d13f02508d78321f2c0601400bf327e651468a","tid":51172,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"無幾耐之前，英超球會水晶宮喺官網宣佈，正式解僱主帥柏祖，睇黎佢今次真係大把時間跳舞啦！<br />\n<br />\n水晶宮今個夏天先後引入賓迪基、法明尼、湯堅斯同埋文丹達等實力猛將，但係球隊嘅成績就不升反跌，依家排緊英超尾四，距離降班區只有1分之隔，所以水晶宮嘅高層就決定，即時炒咗柏祖！<br />\n<br />\n幾個星期前，柏祖仲實牙實齒話唔怕自己俾人炒，但係聖誕節都未到，佢就俾人炒咗啦，唔知呢啲係咪叫「燈死自己」呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/soccerfunnymoment/%E5%A4%A7%E6%8A%8A%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%B7%B3%E8%88%9E-%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%AE%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E6%9F%8F%E7%A5%96-c1259350.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fsoccerfunnymoment%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258A%258A%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E8%2588%259E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%2599%25B6%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E6%259F%258F%25E7%25A5%2596-c1259350.html&d=K3pybirECIXXbfT7YJ9v5HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e6b55b32\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/soccerfunnymoment/%E5%A4%A7%E6%8A%8A%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%B7%B3%E8%88%9E-%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%AE%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E6%9F%8F%E7%A5%96-c1259350.html</a>"},{"pid":"95f779aa1fed6711fecd61b067eb0813aa352bb9","tid":51172,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:11:51.000Z","msg":"聖誕禮物"},{"pid":"b5a527871219d73cb6bb55754d7b882f6c80b0a8","tid":51172,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"柏袓又然"},{"pid":"d586a72d09150df2f93fa